<section>
  <div class="mx-auto w-full lg:px-24 max-w-7xl md:px-12 items-center px-8 py-24 scroll-mt-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-12">
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-normal tracking-tight text-black font-display">
            Frequently Asked Questions
          </p>
          <p class="text-base mt-4 text-zinc-500">
            Answers to commonly asked questions about our AI chat platform.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        x-data="{
  activeAccordion: '',
  setActiveAccordion(id) {
  this.activeAccordion = (this.activeAccordion == id) ? '' : id
  }
  }"
        class="relative w-full mx-auto font-normal lg:col-span-2"
      >
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-black"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span>What AI models does the platform support?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500 -rotate-[45deg]"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="">
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              Our platform integrates multiple AI models, including GPT-4 and Claude, to provide versatile and powerful interactions tailored to your needs.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span>How do I manage my prompts effectively?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="" style="display: none;">
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              Use our prompt management features to organize and store frequently used prompts. This helps streamline interaction and improves response consistency.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span>Can I use the platform for content generation?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="" style="display: none;">
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              Absolutely! Our AI can help in generating high-quality content, including articles, blogs, and creative works, tailored to your specifications.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span>How secure is my data on the platform?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="" style="display: none;">
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              We prioritize your privacy and security with robust encryption and data protection measures, ensuring your information is safe.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
          :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500': activeAccordion!=id }"
          class="cursor-pointer group text-zinc-600 hover:text-accent-500"
        >
          <button
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
          >
            <span>Is there support for multiple users?</span>
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-500"
              :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
            >
          </button>
          <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="" style="display: none;">
            <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-zinc-500">
              Yes, our platform is designed to support multiple users, allowing team collaboration and shared access to AI resources.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>